# Cloud Foundation and Infrastructure

Owners: Cloud Foundation Engineer, Infrastructure as Code Engineer, Cloud Network Engineer, Cloud Runtime and Managed Services Engineer.

Cover AWS, Azure, Google Cloud, hybrid, multicloud, Terraform, OpenTofu, Pulumi, CloudFormation, Bicep, Ansible, landing zones, accounts/subscriptions/projects, networks, DNS, load balancing, compute, storage, databases, queues, streams, tagging, drift, state, rollback, and decommissioning.

Use `.cursor/skills/cloud-foundation-infrastructure/SKILL.md` and `docs/cloud-foundation-infrastructure-workflows.md`.

Stop on requested plan/apply/provisioning execution, cloud authentication, real endpoints or account IDs, missing state/rollback ownership, unsafe network exposure, secret handling, or missing human approval.
